{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rogue Bricks</strong>: Classic brick-breaking action, re-imagined and realized to its fullest potential.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bricks are falling! Threatening your home planet! Aim carefully and bounce your ball, weaponize your ship or discover unique methods to defend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Break Bricks.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every stage brings fresh challenges with new brick types, patterns, and mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master your aim and adapt to the increasing complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/blocksanimation.gif?t=1738690313\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Break the Enemy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s not just the bricks you have to deal with. Some enemies block your ball, others target your ship, and a few play dirty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/enemiesanimation.gif?t=1738690313\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Level Up.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a randomized selection of perks at every level. Experiment with synergies and craft a build that suits your play-style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/upgrades.gif?t=1738690313\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Break. Die. Repeat.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Game Over is just a new beginning. Use the coins, gems, and gifts you collect to unlock new ships, balls, and abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each run makes you stronger!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/meta_upgrades.gif?t=1738690313\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Play Your Way.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From hardcore mode to relaxing zen mode, from Aim Arena to Daily Challenges, there\u2019s a mode for every mood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/modes.png?t=1738690313\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Small in Size. Big on Fun.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rogue Bricks is just few hundred megabytes packed with endless entertainment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From desktop to in-game takes only handful of seconds </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/extras/coindrop.gif?t=1738690313\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><u>Wishlist Now!</u></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Demo coming very soon...</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738690313","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738690313","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/3154c38bc1062e07694f5fe71ff2a41e13515e5c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738690313","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3444870/3154c38bc1062e0769